reviews.text:
Nice recipe! I added 2 drops of FLV per 10ml, and it's really helped the lime stick around. When I mix another bottle, I'll drop it down to 1d per 10ml, because at the current amount, it added almost a lime you get from the lime tootsie rolls. Either way, the strawberry has stuck around, and carries itself well against the lime-aid background.&#xD;
&#xD;
Shake and vape was good, but did have that slight harshness from the FA cold pressed, but about a week later, this has turned into something beautiful. Thanks again,
